prompts.frontCover: **photo-b0577141-0cb4-43c9-ac9a-5b1c08be0ed1** A dynamic comic book style greeting card front. The scene is a vibrant, sun-drenched beach with stylized waves and a clear blue sky. In the foreground, the person on the left from the photo (Lao Lao) is depicted as a comic book hero, standing triumphantly with hands on hips and a big, cheerful smile. The person on the right from the photo (Jordan) is playfully illustrated as a loyal canine sidekick, sitting adoringly next to Lao Lao, wearing a small party hat and holding a bone with a gift tag attached that says "To: Lao Lao". Both are drawn in a clean, flat 2D comic art style with bold outlines and a vibrant color palette, maintaining the clothing from the photo (a light blue sweatshirt and a brown hoodie, logos removed). Surrounding them are classic comic book action elements: a "KAPOW!" sound effect bubble near a rogue wave splashing, and a "ZING!" effect by the brightly shining sun. In the center of the scene, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". Halftone dots are used for shading to enhance the retro comic book feel. The overall composition is energetic, humorous, and full of action.
